OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1783700376
OL,3,CFormer resident criticises report into
OL,4,Ccouncil's handling of evacuation
OL,6,FA former resident of Barton House in
OL,7,FBristol who was forced to leave her
OL,8,Fhome at short notice in 2023 has
OL,9,Fcriticised a report into the council's
OL,10,Fhandling of the tower block evacuation.
OL,12,FFadumo Farah told ITV News: "I still
OL,13,Fsupport a lot of people who are either
OL,14,Fhousing association or council tenants
OL,15,Fand I can see the pattern is the same
OL,16,Fthing - people complaining about damp
OL,17,For mould and not being taken seriously.
OL,19,F"They want you to trust them but when
OL,20,Fyou provide all the medical evidence,
OL,21,Fthey still say that's not enough."
OL,26,@tD@]OU}D@bO]
