OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1783700376
OL,3,CFormer resident criticises report into
OL,4,Ccouncil's handling of evacuation
OL,6,FIt follows an independent review into
OL,7,Fthe emergency evacuation of Barton
OL,8,FHouse in Bristol in November 2023,
OL,9,Fwhich found poor leadership impacted
OL,10,Fthe decision to evacuate the building.
OL,12,FIn November 2023, more than 400
OL,13,Fresidents at Barton House on Barton
OL,14,FHill were told to pack a bag and leave
OL,15,Ftheir home - with just a few hours
OL,16,Fnotice.
OL,18,FA survey had revealed that structural
OL,19,Fissues could put the building at risk
OL,20,Fof collapse in the event of a fire.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,407,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1783700376
OL,3,CFormer resident criticises report into
OL,4,Ccouncil's handling of evacuation
OL,6,FYet concerns about the structure and
OL,7,Ffire safety of the ageing building had
OL,8,Fbeen reported as far back as 2019.
OL,10,FMs Farah told ITV News: "It took a
OL,11,Ftoll on me. I was working, doing my
OL,12,Fmaster's (degree) and I had to stop
OL,13,Feverything to deal with the whole
OL,14,Fthing that was happening.
OL,16,F"It's not only the evacuation - we
OL,17,Fended up going to a hotel, (where we)
OL,18,Fhad a neural outbreak where all the
OL,19,Fchildren had diarrhoea and were
OL,20,Fvomiting.
OL,26,@tD@JpmtD@QpnyD@\pmyD@epn
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,407,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1783700376
OL,3,CFormer resident criticises report into
OL,4,Ccouncil's handling of evacuation
OL,6,FThe former Barton House resident
OL,7,Fdescribes feeling "segregated" at the
OL,8,Fhotel.
OL,10,F"There was a certain area that we have
OL,11,Fto eat and stay and our children were
OL,12,Fnot allowed to run around near the
OL,13,Fpaying guests".
OL,15,FThe authors of the report, carried out
OL,16,Fby Altair Consultancy and Advisory
OL,17,FServices, concluded that the
OL,18,Fevacuation was "right on safety
OL,19,Fgrounds" but weaknesses in how it was
OL,20,Fcarried out led to "avoidable harm".
OL,26,@uD@NO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,407,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1783700376
OL,3,CFormer resident criticises report into
OL,4,Ccouncil's handling of evacuation
OL,6,FThe report, commissioned by Bristol
OL,7,FCity Council, found that the lessons
OL,8,Flearned from the evacuation were as
OL,9,Ffollows:
OL,11,FThe report continued that Bristol City
OL,12,FCouncil has made improvements to its
OL,13,Fleadership capacity as a result. It's
OL,14,Falso created plans for a Housing
OL,15,FStrategy and Assurance Division, which
OL,16,Fwill provide a "stronger" and more
OL,17,F"risk-oriented approach" in future
OL,18,Fincidents.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,407,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1783700376
OL,3,CFormer resident criticises report into
OL,4,Ccouncil's handling of evacuation
OL,6,FThe authors provided key
OL,7,Frecommendations, including improving
OL,8,Fprocesses for acting on government
OL,9,Fadvice, training staff in risk and
OL,10,Fsafety, and working with residents on
OL,11,Fthe future of the building.
OL,13,FIt also recommended improvements to
OL,14,Fhow the council communicates with
OL,15,Fresidents about major incidents.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,407,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1783700376
OL,3,CFormer resident criticises report into
OL,4,Ccouncil's handling of evacuation
OL,6,FThe council say that a new Resident
OL,7,FVoice Strategy has been set up, which
OL,8,Fcreates a more "inclusive" and
OL,9,F"transparent" approach to engagement,
OL,10,Fincluding more opportunities for
OL,11,Fresidents to get involved in decision-
OL,12,Fmaking.
OL,14,FIn a statement, Councillor Barry
OL,15,FParsons, Chair of the Homes and
OL,16,FHousing Delivery Committee, said: "I
OL,17,Fwould like to thank everyone who
OL,18,Fcontributed to this review,
OL,19,Fparticularly the residents of Barton
OL,20,FHouse who shared their experiences so
OL,21,Fopenly and honestly.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,407,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1783700376
OL,3,CFormer resident criticises report into
OL,4,Ccouncil's handling of evacuation
OL,6,F"Reliving such a difficult period will
OL,7,Fnot have been easy, and their
OL,8,Fwillingness to speak candidly was
OL,9,Fessential in helping us understand
OL,10,Fboth the strengths of the response and
OL,11,Fwhere things could have been better,
OL,12,Fand the lasting impact this had.
OL,14,F"This report reflects the reality of a
OL,15,Fsituation. Although concerns about the
OL,16,Fstructure of the building were raised
OL,17,Fin 2022, they were not escalated or
OL,18,Facted on quickly enough.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,407,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40609
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1783700376
OL,3,CFormer resident criticises report into
OL,4,Ccouncil's handling of evacuation
OL,6,F"However, when new information
OL,7,Fsuggesting a fire could result in the
OL,8,Fbuilding collapsing was shared, those
OL,9,Finvolved were determined to protect
OL,10,Fresidents and made the best decisions
OL,11,Fpossible in exceptionally challenging
OL,12,Fand fast-changing circumstances.
OL,14,F"The review rightly recognises the
OL,15,Fimpact the evacuation and the months
OL,16,Fthat followed had on residents, and we
OL,17,Facknowledge the distress and
OL,18,Funcertainty many people experienced.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,407,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40610
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1783700376
OL,3,CFormer resident criticises report into
OL,4,Ccouncil's handling of evacuation
OL,6,F"We accept the report's findings and
OL,7,Frecommendations in full. The report
OL,8,Fprovides clear recommendations which
OL,9,Fwe will learn from.
OL,11,F"The changes already being made across
OL,12,Four housing services, alongside our
OL,13,Fnew Resident Voice Strategy and
OL,14,Fstrengthened governance arrangements,
OL,15,Fdemonstrate our commitment to doing
OL,16,Fthat.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,407,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40611
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1783700376
OL,3,CFormer resident criticises report into
OL,4,Ccouncil's handling of evacuation
OL,6,F"Our focus is on continuing to rebuild
OL,7,Ftrust, listening to residents, and
OL,8,Fmaking sure the lessons from Barton
OL,9,FHouse contribute to meaningful and
OL,10,Flasting improvements for all residents
OL,11,Facross Bristol."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
